00:09:29,260 --> 00:09:34,440
causality here, and it's worth taking a moment to reflect on the role played by the speed c

143
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:40,540
in all of this explanation. c is the speed determining how long it takes for an accelerating

144
00:09:40,540 --> 00:09:46,400
charge to induce a force on any other charge. Even if there's material in the way, whether that

145
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:51,140
material has an index of refraction bigger than one or less than one, that amount of time that

